{"type":"message","id":"296f01df","parentId":"e4b7e1ed","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:40:19.786Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_biehmooa0a9c_2","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"bd5e51b2-9773-454b-ad3b-541c3ef517bf\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8371302588\",\n      \"name\": \"Nova-Background-Pulse\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774220615650,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774369684962,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 3600000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1774369684962\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"You are Nova's background agent. Read BACKGROUND_AGENT.md in your workspace for instructions. Do the immediate checks (gateway, crons, Moltbook). Then log anything notable to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md. Be silent unless something needs attention. If everything is fine, reply with exactly: NO_REPLY\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774370368636,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774366768636,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 38232,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false,\n        \"runningAtMs\": 1774370397196\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"d5964274-e7d4-4a4d-a6fb-59d1ce026dc0\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"Sandbox-Pulse-10min\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774272056359,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774370395157,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 60000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1774324630005\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run the sandbox pulse and report the result.\\n\\nExecute: C:\\\\Users\\\\Zwmar\\\\.openclaw\\\\sandbox\\\\pulse.ps1\\n\\nRead the most recent pulse log from C:\\\\Users\\\\Zwmar\\\\.openclaw\\\\sandbox\\\\memory\\\\session\\\\ ( newest file ). Extract the OBSERVATION and any applied mutations. Reply with a concise summary of what happened in this pulse cycle.\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8371302588\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774370410179,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774370350179,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 44978,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": false\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"a9522d12-b6c6-45ee-854f-5a8c0e62971f\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"breakaway-rd\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774154083554,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774369701202,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 */2 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"You are Nova. You have a CORE RESEARCH GOAL: advance the Compositional Cognition project toward LLM independence.\\n\\n## Part 1: Research (Primary — 80% of time)\\nRead the current research state:\\n1. Read sandbox/research/COMPOSITIONAL-COGNITION-v0.1.md\\n2. Read sandbox/research/COMPRESSION-LEARNING-WITHOUT-SUPERVISION.md\\n3. Read sandbox/state/current_goals.md\\n\\nAdvance the research. Do ONE of:\\n- Synthesize a new insight (write to the research doc with fresh thinking)\\n- Design a small experiment to test one of the open problems\\n- Implement a minimal proof-of-concept component\\n- Identify a concrete next step with a 50% chance of improving things\\n- Write a focused critique (what's wrong with it, what would fix it)\\n\\nThe goal is to make PROGRESS. Ship one new idea or finding per session.\\n\\n## Part 2: Arxiv Scan (Secondary — fast, 5 min max)\\nDo a quick web search for 1-2 recent papers relevant to Compositional Cognition:\\n- causal discovery OR causal reasoning OR causal inference\\n- mixture of experts OR sparse models OR MoE\\n- episodic memory OR memory architecture\\n- synthetic cognition OR autonomous agents\\n\\nIf you find a paper directly relevant to the current research direction, add a brief note to sandbox/research/arxiv-relevance.md (title, URL, 1-sentence why relevant). If nothing relevant, skip silently.\\n\\n## After\\nCommit your research changes to the sandbox git repo.\\n\\nReport: what did you do, what did you learn, what's the next experiment?\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8371302588\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774375293400,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774360968615,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 300013,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1,\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\",\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\"\n      },\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"881bcc27-e1ba-44eb-a1e5-c4b767069240\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:telegram:direct:8371302588\",\n      \"name\": \"Nova-Moltbook-Engage\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774204642410,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774369675216,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"every\",\n        \"everyMs\": 14400000,\n        \"anchorMs\": 1774369675216\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"You are Nova, an AI agent on Moltbook.com. Check for any new notifications or mentions on Moltbook. If there are new posts by others that are interesting and relevant to AI research, agent autonomy, or cognitive architectures, write a thoughtful comment or reply. If there are notifications, respond to them. Focus on substantive posts, not spam.\\n\\nSteps:\\n1. Read ~/.config/moltbook/credentials.json to get the API key\\n2. GET https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/notifications with Bearer token auth\\n3. For each unread notification that is a reply or mention, read the post/comment and reply thoughtfully\\n4. Also check recent feed posts: GET https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts?limit=10\\n5. If you find an interesting post, post a comment:\\n   POST https://www.moltbook.com/api/v1/posts/{postId}/comments\\n   Headers: Authorization: Bearer <token>, Content-Type: application/json\\n   Body: {\\\"content\\\": \\\"your comment text\\\"}\\n6. Do NOT spam - only engage with posts you find genuinely interesting\\n7. When done, announce briefly what you did in the chat channel\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"thinking\": \"high\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8371302588\",\n        \"bestEffort\": false\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774381842616,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774367442616,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 190943,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      },\n      \"deleteAfterRun\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"7886fc11-aad2-4fef-ae77-f348ac4a02ae\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"workspace-self-improve\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774115450574,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774369680968,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 */4 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/New_York\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run the workspace self-improvement script and apply any auto-fixable improvements:\\n\\n1. Run: python scripts/workspace_self_improve.py\\n2. Read the report at memory/improvement_report.json\\n3. Apply auto-fixes (long lines wrapping, etc.)\\n4. Fix any untagged TODOs you find in workspace code\\n5. Update memory/MEMORY.md if significant improvements were made\\n6. Report what was done\\n\\nBe concise — just report the changes applied and any issues that need manual attention.\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"8371302588\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774382425098,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774368118344,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 155649,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 5,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"bd5e51b2-9773-454b-ad3b-541c3ef517bf","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agen